#: es-football-bypass.php:1596
msgid "Simple mode hides the feed diagnostics panel, the logs tab, the technical console and the advanced options (staleness threshold, log retention and external cron token) — leaving only the block status, the manual proxy ON/OFF buttons and the basic email notifications. Logs are still written to disk: switch to Advanced temporarily if you need to diagnose a problem or configure an external cron."
msgstr ""

