msgid "Minimum number of distinct ISPs (providers) with currently blocked IPs needed to consider there is a real mass block (1-20, default 2). Lower values are more sensitive; 1 triggers on any single-ISP glitch. Only applies when the feed publishes ISP information; ignored otherwise."
msgstr ""

